WEBVTT

00:01:59.260 --> 00:02:01.196
and for the rest of us, too.

00:02:02.474 --> 00:02:05.664
Now, I bet you're skeptical
about this idea.

00:02:06.204 --> 00:02:08.800
And honestly, I was, too.

00:02:09.330 --> 00:02:12.958
I mean, there must be a reason
the voting age is 18.

00:02:12.982 --> 00:02:15.577
(Laughter)

00:02:16.188 --> 00:02:19.479
How could children possibly
understand complex ideas

00:02:19.503 --> 00:02:21.887
such as the affordable housing crisis

00:02:21.911 --> 00:02:25.045
or how to develop
a transportation master plan?

00:02:25.935 --> 00:02:29.080
And even if they had ideas,
wouldn't they be childish?

00:02:29.688 --> 00:02:31.061
Or unreasonable?